{"tid":2320052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輝瑞疫苗效用數據被盗取 歐洲藥物管理局遭黑客攻擊","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:58:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f0b49f6a49e778afc7ce5b351a3c804b9fbfbc","tid":2320052,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"美國藥廠輝瑞及其德國夥伴 BioNTech 開發的疫苗，在早前正式開始在英國進行接種。然而，該企業表示，有黑客攻擊歐洲藥物管理局（European Medicine Agency, EMA）系統，試圖偷取與病毒疫苗有關的文件。不過，局方交代目前已展開全面調查，並強調可正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n美國藥廠輝瑞及其德國夥伴 BioNTech 指，歐洲藥物管理局（European Medicine Agency, EMA）需要審查其研發的兩款疫苗安全性及效用，故在早期曾向 EMA 監管部門提交疫苗的部分文件。不過，其證實早前獲局方通知，有黑客攻擊 EMA 伺服器，並曾非法取閱輝瑞疫苗的文件。<br />\n<br />\n輝瑞及  BioNTech 表示，EMA 未有交代攻擊事件詳情，如受到甚麼類型的黑客攻擊、如何攻擊等等，只指部份疫苗數據被盗。不過，藥廠表示，相關數據不涉及測試參加者的個人資料，只涉及疫苗機制、效用、風險、已知副作用等，並指 EMA 目前已展開全面調查。<br />\n<br />\nEMA 強調當局仍然可正常運作，其亦向藥廠保證，審批程序的時間表不會受到事件影響。預料審核工作將 12 月 29 日完成。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/10/ema-hack/life-tech/health/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2Fema-hack%2Flife-tech%2Fhealth%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=178be24f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/10/ema-hack/life-tech/health/</a>"},{"pid":"f40da477db580641a53bb71a0a2e79920daf3af0","tid":2320052,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:23:27.000Z","msg":"又偷"},{"pid":"87de08e522a4f440d552b83d50c071525d337ef2","tid":2320052,"uid":52594,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"強國好快可以自煮研發出來"},{"pid":"83ce63e1fb430b3bb4b8eb6b6f077cfc7a644caa","tid":2320052,"uid":38518,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:25:12.000Z","msg":"支那咁耐都無data原來係等緊偷"},{"pid":"caa92ef8a70294fdb241ecb49e6cf6acc6c9def1","tid":2320052,"uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">偷到手了，只怪你們太單純</span>"},{"pid":"923001ecc0eebbec30cf0b3d875f5d63914cc147","tid":2320052,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"弱智都唔係第一次"},{"pid":"96f713a38b45c8f8f24eeabc74535b638616a0eb","tid":2320052,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"重有邊個國家會偷，大家都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db292df688fd88345d9629d0695e5875d9f7f4c1","tid":2320052,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"所以點解咁乞人憎 <br />\n真係有理由<br />\n<br />\n偷呃拐騙最撚叻既國家"},{"pid":"751cc4171982b76cf1afdf37778bf9617bc3cced","tid":2320052,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:58:03.000Z","msg":"下一個用mrna技術既一定係偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}